:0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T08:36:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>見到有某個組織有集會<br />\n但果個集會係已經被警察反對了<br />\n所以係非法的<br />\n各位一旦去左就有機會被捕<br />\n一生留有案底<br />\n真係值得?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n利申決定聽你講唔去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我個POST係公正無立場<br />\n只係想大家自己諗清楚<br />\n得果10幾20幾歲<br />\n就留有案底<br />\n咩前途都無晒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n決定唔去啦"},{"pid":"4404b7b7f160dd5ccca254c8cdf0b92c3aa3c876","tid":303492,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T08:37:59.000Z","msg":"加力SIR有冇射波呀呢幾日"},{"pid":"e0ecc00ccee2bb291d1bb9292151d8d573ba55fa","tid":303492,"uid":54183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T08:39:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c03fc4e5f6349f6b3fbff1e0b98911a3553d39cb","tid":303492,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T08:40:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第245章 《公安條例》 第18條 非法集結<br />\n<br />\n對照任何兩個版本<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(1)凡有3人或多於3人集結在一起，作出擾亂秩序的行為或作出帶有威嚇性、侮辱性或挑撥性的行為，意圖導致或相當可能導致任何人合理地害怕如此集結的人會破壞社會安寧，或害怕他們會藉以上的行為激使其他人破壞社會安寧，他們即屬非法集結。 (由1970年第31號第11條修訂)<br />\n(2)集結的人如作出如上述般的行為，則即使其原來的集結是合法的，亦無關重要。<br />\n(3)任何人如參與憑藉第(1)款屬非法集結的集結，即犯非法集結罪 &mdash;&mdash;  (由1970年第31號第11條修訂)<br />\n(a)一經循公訴程序定罪，可處監禁5年；及<br />\n(b)一經循簡易程序定罪，可處第2級罰款及監禁3年。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不如貼埋上網屌柒支共犯咩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/30/164053_67eca90cddd5c7b757a8eee4c5034582.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F30%2F164053_67eca90cddd5c7b757a8eee4c5034582.jpg&h=ad731524&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/30/164054_1be22268c0a5ed044c0f6f62d3cf4451.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F30%2F164054_1be22268c0a5ed044c0f6f62d3cf4451.jpg&h=cb19ea21&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"49a3ea5fc40a24ebc1c24326e85fb75c17b9552e","tid":303492,"uid":106498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T08:43:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>第245章 《公安條例》 第18條 非法集結<br />\n<br />\n對照任何兩個版本<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(1)凡有3人或多於3人集結在一起，作出擾亂秩序的行為或作出帶有威嚇性、侮辱性或挑撥性的行為，意圖導致或相當可能導致任何人合理地害怕如此集結的人會破壞社會安寧，或害怕他們會藉以上的行為激使其他人破壞社會安寧，他們即屬非法集結。 (由1970年第31號第11條修訂)<br />\n(2)集結的人如作出如上述般的行為，則即使其原來的集結是合法的，亦無關重要。<br />\n(3)任何人如參與憑藉第(1)款屬非法集結的集結，即犯非法集結罪 &mdash;&mdash;  (由1970年第31號第11條修訂)<br />\n(a)一經循公訴程序定罪，可處監禁5年；及<br />\n(b)一經循簡易程序定罪，可處第2級罰款及監禁3年。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不如貼埋上網屌柒支共犯咩法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n[mg]<a href=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/30/164053_67eca90cddd5c7b757a8eee4c5034582.jpg[/img][img]http://mg.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/30/164054_1be22268c0a5ed044c0f6f62d3cf4451.jpg[/mg]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F30%2F164053_67eca90cddd5c7b757a8eee4c5034582.jpg%5B%2Fimg%5D%5Bimg%5Dhttp%3A%2F%2Fmg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F30%2F164054_1be22268c0a5ed044c0f6f62d3cf4451.jpg%5B%2Fmg%5D&d=yPbTbF%2BwQaTv4I4YfP4w1tr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=1facadef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/30/164053_67eca90cddd5c7b757a8eee4c5034582.jpg[/img][img]http://mg.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/30/164054_1be22268c0a5ed044c0f6f62d3cf4451.jpg[/mg]</a></blockquote><br />\n我無可能話你犯咩法<br />\n你係唔係犯法只有法庭可講<br />\n我只可提你地做呢D野係好大機會犯法<br />\n要三思"},{"pid":"9d5596620c8617243456fecce808f450664a5403","tid":303492,"uid":62494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T08:45:29.000Z","msg":"Shoot to kill"},{"pid":"99c715ae9c3ad5e9256d65660d7555bf927061cc","tid":303492,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,